<pre data-sourcepos="7:1-9:3" data-canonical-lang="crontab" class="code highlight js-syntax-highlight language-plaintext" v-pre="true"><code is:raw><span id="LC1" class="line" lang="plaintext">*/10 * * * * /home/user/.asdf/shims/ruby /usr/local/bin/dns_updater</span></code></pre>
